    public class DomainBPlusTreeJVSTM<T extends AbstractDomainObject>
extends DomainBPlusTreeJVSTM_Base
    A DomainBPlusTree with a JVSTM-specific optimization to obtain the size(). The size is kept in a slot of the DomainBPlusTreeData, so it's access is O(1).
